s=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6BhxLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6BhxLH.png&h=17ed08dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YHaezY2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYHaezY2.png&h=2cf666bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaJcmD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaJcmD3.png&h=b13d88e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZCMq5J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZCMq5J.png&h=ce1fe97e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKgNaxo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKgNaxo.png&h=4588b45e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xtLGD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xtLGD4.png&h=7f2ffa76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjTPoSp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjTPoSp.png&h=a2884bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTMdQxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTMdQxp.png&h=4639d744&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fz6tEqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffz6tEqK.png&h=82c415a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajfRCcq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajfRCcq.png&h=9a795320&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd4b23e9d60b2b051dc9c3bdcd556a634adb51e7","tid":1990244,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fa35cbfcad20fa24324d2f58819f269fa1f2fb2","tid":1990244,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"322ce08bae7146d39c8cacaecd73a9e63f309d34","tid":1990244,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"從種種跡象看，伊朗或北韓將會成為美國下一個目標。不幸地，北韓可能最毛遭殃。北韓的存亡，將直接影響東南亞的戰略格局，並對中美日後的戰略態勢有重大的影響。<br />\n<br />\n五十六年前，毛澤東在新中國成立不過一年時，毅然「抗美援朝」，傾國家之全力，終逼和了美國，東北從此得北韓為緩衝區，並且牽制了日本、南韓、美國在東北的勢力，鴨綠江得以安寧。<br />\n<br />\n目前，朝鮮局勢並不樂觀。韓戰有可能再次爆發。這次我認為還是不能失掉北韓，一個統一的韓國永遠比一個分裂的韓國對中國更不利。<br />\n<br />\n美國若成功吞併北韓，東北則面對日本、南韓、美國三股勢力聯手的圍堵，東北形勢笈笈可危，到時美國一發難，中國將要同時面對東西夾擊，打上台灣印度可能乘機分一杯羹，形勢更雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n第二次韓戰，我們要面對的不只是美軍和南韓，還有台灣很可能乘機發難，還有來自西面國土的問題(別有用心勢力煽動少數民族動亂)，甚至要面對日本及東南亞諸國。可謂腹背受敵，牽一髮動全身。然而，若光著眼看北韓被美利堅帝國所滅，問題不只沒有解決，反而會更嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n美利堅帝國用來攻擊北韓的藉口大概又是那些莫須有的理由，北韓有沒有核武器並不重要，無中可生有，北韓有沒有大殺力武器也不重要，伊拉克前車可鑑，普遍人民是短視愚昧的，只要啟動美國式傳媒機器灌輸，黑可以說成白，白也可染黑。其實世界上擁最多大殺傷力武器的就是美國，真正的恐怖主義來自美國，真正的邪惡軸心也是美國。<br />\n<br />\n北韓問題關乎我國之核心利益，並對我國未來戰略形勢影響甚巨，中央得想一個合切的辦法去解決。<br />\n<br />\n「起來吧！ 雄糾糾﹑氣昂昂，志願軍再過鴨綠江，抵禦外悔於彼方。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者：香港高登社會主義大學駐中共中央新華社專業時事評論員<br />\n屍屠嘩"},{"pid":"6bbc10127040281a67d045148a07421d29e19d7e","tid":1990244,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"da93e896825c53cee32220dedcac55f5ba199cd1","tid":1990244,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0178311d785f72703d63f168bfb590174db23f6d","tid":1990244,"uid":258578,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"準備好喇，反正今次唔滅你班垃圾中共人族，你哋都會嚟滅我哋族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2756a0189f8bae6196b7516a94bfd801333e1660","tid":1990244,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4ebcfe2becb240c2a7f537ca40f202265c26d4a","tid":1990244,"uid":356930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:52:05.000Z","msg":"人造人19號，見一次笑一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fe67f34abb9f4b731a7ae7f52f6411983fb0ae","tid":1990244,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0178311d785f72703d63f168bfb590174db23f6d","tid":1990244,"uid":258578,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"Block."}]}